title: PowerArchiver 2013 RC2 Build 14.00.30 [PL] [KEYGEN FFF]
description:
PowerArchiver known program for compression, decompression and handling compressed file archives. Supports multiple file formats: ZIP, CAB, LHA (LHZ), TAR, TAR.GZ, tar.bz2, BH, RAR, ACE, ARJ, GZIP, ARC, ZOO. It has built-in support for UUE encoded files and XXE. It can create self-extracting archives ZIP, RAR, ACE and others. The program has a very easy-to-use interface with many freely modified options, integrates well with OS Explorer. It has tools to convert, repair and split archives. It is also possible to change the appearance of the toolbar so many additional skins.

-----------------------------------------
Manufacturer: ConeXware Inc.
Operating System: Windows 98/Me/NT/2000/XP/Vista/7
